like":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T17:39:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我記得事後發現佢好似有拍，咁啱影唔倒<br />\n再者有冇拍好小事，不嬲覺得拍手好例行公事</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個姿態好明顯係無拍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  睇埋佢係黃百鳴隔離基本都解釋了一切<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  就係連例行公事都唔做？公開場合講你同事升職你會唔會黑面坐係度"},{"pid":"01e44c8354036fa0d7dcb3d63d3b32c90feb6915","tid":193992,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T17:41:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我記得事後發現佢好似有拍，咁啱影唔倒<br />\n再者有冇拍好小事，不嬲覺得拍手好例行公事</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n會員蝦兵蟹將有妄想症"},{"pid":"4b241853e68428952790eff7f412fe34c378bd90","tid":193992,"uid":81771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T18:01:55.000Z","msg":"好撚悶 乜撚野都要講政治"},{"pid":"cbcae74972c65cf0cc4c8756e14745c6f314f2f6","tid":193992,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T18:18:09.000Z","msg":"佢敢講已經勇啦"},{"pid":"a761080957c7f18a4d6e581f5aee89a3664a2a2b","tid":193992,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T18:24:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9edc4d591ece0d1c957ba7aee625c3f1f8e1fcb9","tid":193992,"uid":37666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T22:16:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢敢講已經勇啦</blockquote><br />\n咪係 如果講政治<br />\n屌都屌志偉先啦 <br />\n捐錢比七警喎"},{"pid":"62d990c33b6d6a68273f38dafd187c82dd7a6060","tid":193992,"uid":47210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T22:49:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢敢講已經勇啦</blockquote><br />\n唔係敢唔敢講, 係咁做份人顯得好撚假"},{"pid":"02f0c9ca17023a5de16fd3e9175d7e47e8290530","tid":193992,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T22:51:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>佢敢講已經勇啦</blockquote><br />\n唔係敢唔敢講, 係咁做份人顯得好撚假</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢其實去盡d大可唔講<br />\n佢講我覺覺得算係咁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n始終十年都唔關佢事"},{"pid":"3de0a7377c8e650fd9a92e0bb9d2bdd804f967fc","tid":193992,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T00:09:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好撚悶 乜撚野都要講政治</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港太多你呢種人"},{"pid":"d6000b61f71f72e6027b17f712709d6984de3ff4","tid":193992,"uid":985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T00:13:12.000Z","msg":"睇過十年，唔講題材，真係唔值得攞獎。<br />\n唔係咁有話題性，應該睇左一半就熄mon"},{"pid":"caeac8beab4296be39dd61f2d955e0caa91dcc0d","tid":193992,"uid":55981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T01:38:51.000Z","msg":"屌你文革咩<br />\n唔拍手又要批鬥<br />\n咁你同唱國歌唔喊比人拉出嚟屌有咩分別<br />\n成日話最憎大陸<br />\n但自己思想行為同紅衛兵一撚樣"},{"pid":"328a82a418a909094ccb84d4f4bd41650c7c7090","tid":193992,"uid":3206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T02:06:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>佢敢講已經勇啦</blockquote><br />\n咪係 如果講政治<br />\n屌都屌志偉先啦 <br />\n捐錢比七警喎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n少年太年輕 佢敢講係因為果位導演無被封殺 咁即係仲係清白之身 過哂風頭火勢咪又可以做朋友囉<br />\n呢啲就係佢地偽人既世態炎涼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96aa502bd69ba69d0a47782f4240d5cfe42cc07a","tid":193992,"uid":3206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T02:10:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好撚悶 乜撚野都要講政治</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港太多你呢種人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n重點係閱讀理解0分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我只係想講佢個人幾假 戥導演不值 無諗住拉埋政治黎講囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過 你唔講政治 唔代表政治唔影響你 你可以做你港豬既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c6a0b0019b3b90ab6d90e350c2bb8220670634f","tid":193992,"uid":3206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T02:12:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇過十年，唔講題材，真係唔值得攞獎。<br />\n唔係咁有話題性，應該睇左一半就熄mon</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n覺得唔值係一回事 大方恭喜得獎者係另一回事<br />\n坐得在場就要尊重場合 尊重人地係基本人格掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2dd52cf37a5ab6dfbdab372a607a3612efbd1cd","tid":193992,"uid":3206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T02:18:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌你文革咩<br />\n唔拍手又要批鬥<br />\n咁你同唱國歌唔喊比人拉出嚟屌有咩分別<br />\n成日話最憎大陸<br />\n但自己思想行為同紅衛兵一撚樣</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n宜家係講緊佢份人係有事就驚死惹上身 唔係拍唔拍個手咁簡單 無事兼幫到佢時就即係講到幾感恩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n見風轉舵 假到咁既偽人唔屌得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3731ae9fc6024f3f88980c8b96ce32673caa4228","tid":193992,"uid":44461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T02:18:36.000Z","msg":"唔係第一次<br />\n<br />\n金像獎司儀林家棟　狂寸本土電影《點對點》　導演斥「欠基本尊重」<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/culture/%E9%87%91%E5%83%8F%E7%8D%8E%E5%8F%B8%E5%84%80%E6%9E%97%E5%AE%B6%E6%A3%9F-%E7%8B%82%E5%AF%B8%E6%9C%AC%E5%9C%9F%E9%9B%BB%E5%BD%B1-%E9%BB%9E%E5%B0%8D%E9%BB%9E-%E5%B0%8E%E6%BC%94%E6%96%A5-%E6%AC%A0%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E5%B0%8A%E9%87%8D/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fculture%2F%25E9%2587%2591%25E5%2583%258F%25E7%258D%258E%25E5%258F%25B8%25E5%2584%2580%25E6%259E%2597%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E6%25A3%259F-%25E7%258B%2582%25E5%25AF%25B8%25E6%259C%25AC%25E5%259C%259F%25E9%259B%25BB%25E5%25BD%25B1-%25E9%25BB%259E%25E5%25B0%258D%25E9%25BB%259E-%25E5%25B0%258E%25E6%25BC%2594%25E6%2596%25A5-%25E6%25AC%25A0%25E5%259F%25BA%25E6%259C%25AC%25E5%25B0%258A%25E9%2587%258D%2F&d=Eps995EZp4R4ibMzYmnfr9r9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=27ea20c0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fculture%2F%25E9%2587%2591%25E5%2583%258F%25E7%258D%258E%25E5%258F%25B8%25